rant if you are selected.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:&#10;0cm;margin-left:11.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-11.35pt\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;\">-</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/support\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:blue\">Support overview (europa.eu)</span></a><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:blue\">:&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Page gathering all support tools (overview, guidance and manuals, FAQ's, helpdesk, support videos)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;&#10;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:11.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-11.35pt\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">F</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">or help related to this call</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">, if you did not find an answer in the various support means</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">, please contact</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">: </span><i><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:red;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE\"><a href=\"mailto